- Update pipe name from CivVPGameState to civv_llm to match orchestrator
- Add minimal JSON parser (JsonValue, JsonParser classes)
- Implement JSON protocol message handling in HandlePipeCommand:
  * action messages (move_unit implemented)
  * get_state messages (placeholder response)
  * end_turn messages
- Update SendTurnData to send turn_start messages per protocol
- Maintain backward compatibility with legacy text-based commands

The implementation follows the protocol specification in docs/protocol.md.
Action results return proper action_result format with state deltas.
Legacy commands (list_units, move_unit, unit_action) still work.

See IMPLEMENTATION_NOTES.md for implementation strategy and next steps.
